Here is the modified merge sort procedure(its run time in theta notation is (nk + nlg(n/k)):
```
void mergesort(int arr[], int p, int r, int k) { // k is the coarseness
	int q = (p + r) / 2;

    if (r - p + 1 &gt; k) { // when the size of the subarray is atmost k, sort using insertion sort
	mergesort(arr, p, q, k);
	mergesort(arr, q + 1, r, k);
        
        merge(arr, p, q, r); // merge is the standard procedure
		
	}
    else {
        insort(arr, p, r); // insort is the standard insertion sort procedure
    }

}
```
